name: 4 Days : small intentions
description:
4Days is a journey along a course of 96 hours of his life. Taking the lessons from previous projects and applying them to the moment, Wessel rides the rails in a hard push to understand...what, exactly? Well, that’s to be found within the con- tents of this book. Twenty nine Small Intentions, moments in life, thought, emotion, mood, vibe. Just some ink on 9x12 pieces of paper. A lot can happen in four days. A lot can be done with the simplest of tools.

First edition
